Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.20,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\pos(419,171)}布類髮飾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.20,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\pos(419,184)}針類髮飾
